OL,3,C'The whole house shook': locals share
OL,4,Cthe reality of living on the A75
OL,6,FScotland's First Minister assures
OL,7,Flocals he will 'explore every possible
OL,8,Fopportunity' to improve safety during
OL,9,Fan A75 focussed visit to Dumfries and
OL,10,FGalloway.
OL,12,FJohn Swinney, MSP for Perthshire North
OL,13,Fand head of the Scottish National
OL,14,FParty, visited Crocketford to explain
OL,15,Fto campaigners what he intends to do
OL,16,Fabout bypassing the two villages of
OL,17,FCrocketford and nearby Springholm -
OL,18,Fwhich the A75 currently runs through.
