OL,3,C'The whole house shook': locals share
OL,4,Cthe reality of living on the A75
OL,6,FThe visit comes as a #5 million study
OL,7,Fto assess where the bypasses should be
OL,8,Fplaced is announced.
OL,10,FCampaigners continue to call for an
OL,11,Fupgrade of the key road, which links
OL,12,FStranraer with Gretna.
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV Border, John Swinney
OL,15,FMSP said: "It's difficult to predict a
OL,16,Ftimescale because there are many
OL,17,Fvariables, such as public local
OL,18,Fenquiries.
