OL,3,C'The whole house shook': locals share
OL,4,Cthe reality of living on the A75
OL,6,F"There is the possibility of smaller,
OL,7,Fmore incremental improvements that
OL,8,Fmight be possible to be taken forward
OL,9,Fto improve safety, and I certainly am
OL,10,Fkeen to ensure we explore every
OL,11,Fpossible opportunity for doing that.
OL,13,F"And then there are other suggestions
OL,14,Fon safety, for example, average speed
OL,15,Fcameras."
