OL,3,C'The whole house shook': locals share
OL,4,Cthe reality of living on the A75
OL,6,FResidents of Crocketford and
OL,7,FSpringholm - the only villages drivers
OL,8,Fpass through from Belfast to London -
OL,9,Fare concerned about the number of
OL,10,Florries which pass through the
OL,11,Fvillages on their way to the ferry
OL,12,Fports near Stranraer.
OL,14,FResidents say the dangers the A75 pose
OL,15,Fto them are very real and believe
OL,16,Fupgrading the A75 will help to
OL,17,Fmitigate the problems.
