OL,3,C'The whole house shook': locals share
OL,4,Cthe reality of living on the A75
OL,6,FTwo years ago Jonathan Johnstone and
OL,7,Fhis wife were getting ready for bed
OL,8,Fwhen a lorry crashed into their house
OL,9,Fjust yards from the road in
OL,10,FCrocketford.
OL,12,F"We were in the bedroom when the truck
OL,13,Fcame over onto its side on top of two
OL,14,Fcars and then slid into our bedroom
OL,15,Fwall," explained Mr Johnstone.
OL,17,F"The whole house shook, the lights
OL,18,Fwent off momentarily, there was
OL,19,Fplaster coming out of the walls.
