OL,3,C'The whole house shook': locals share
OL,4,Cthe reality of living on the A75
OL,6,F"My wife started screaming, 'we've
OL,7,Fjust been hit by a truck!'
OL,9,F"We were scared. We've never
OL,10,Fexperienced anything like that. But we
OL,11,Fwere worried about the guy driving the
OL,12,Ftruck. He was covered in blood."
OL,14,FMr Swinney met with road campaigners
OL,15,Fand stakeholders including Belfast
OL,16,FHarbour, Stena Line and P&O Ferries
OL,17,Fand Galloway and West Dumfries MSP
OL,18,FFinlay Carson.
