OL,3,C'The whole house shook': locals share
OL,4,Cthe reality of living on the A75
OL,6,FWhile the announcement of the #5
OL,7,Fmillion civil engineering report has
OL,8,Fbeen welcomed, locals have
OL,9,Freservations about whether the project
OL,10,Fwill be completed.
OL,12,FAnn Botel, a resident of Crocketford,
OL,13,Fsaid: "At the end of the day it's
OL,14,Fgoing to come down to money and
OL,15,Fwhether they can actually do it.
OL,17,F"It's difficult with the way we are
OL,18,Fplaced, you've got the loch down the
OL,19,Froad, so to get a route to actually
OL,20,Fmake a bypass might be a difficulty."
